Obinna Odogwu, Abakaliki A violent clash between some groups suspected to be political thugs have left two persons dead this morning at Amagu Ikwo community in Ikwo Local Government Area of Ebonyi State. This was even as the corpse of an unknown man was found along the Abakaliki/Enugu Expressway, in front of the second phase of the Federal Teaching Hospital, Abakaliki (FETHA II).  Full details later